<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kopparakecari<hi rend="grantha">panma</hi> rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">je</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">ntra</hi> coḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi> vā<unclear>k</unclear>ku yāṇṭu 3<g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>Āvatu nitta
<lb n="3" break="no"/>viṉotavaḷanāṭṭu Āvūrkkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahma</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">de</hi> yam perālattūr <hi rend="grantha">sa<unclear>bh</unclear>ai</hi> yom tañcā<unclear>vū</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rkkūṟṟattut tañcā<unclear>vū</unclear>rk karun=ti ṭṭaikuṭi
<lb n="6"/><hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi> varkku mūla<hi rend="grantha">bhṛtya</hi> rā[ ṉa <hi rend="grantha">Ādica</hi>] <hi rend="grantha">ṇḍeśca</hi> ra<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va<hi rend="grantha"/>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rkku na<note n="506-3">After na a small portion is not engraved in the original.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Oṭṭik kait<unclear>ti</unclear>ṭṭu Iṭṭu ku<supplied reason="omitted">ṭu</supplied>tta paricā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>vatu Ittevarpakkal nāṅk(ā)ḷ koṇṭa
<lb n="9"/>kācu Eḻupattañcu Ikkācu Eḻupattañ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>cuṅ koṇṭu Ittevarkku can=ti rātitta
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vaṟa Iṟaiyili ceytu kuṭutta nilam I
<lb n="12" break="no"/>vvūr pālāṣriyaṉ parame<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> raṉ
<lb n="13"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>rākavaṉpakkal vilaikoṇṭa
<lb n="14"/>nilam muḷḷaṅkāl Eṉṟu perkū
<lb n="15" break="no"/>vappaṭum nilattukkuk ki<unclear>ḻ</unclear>pār kkellai veḷ
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ḷāṉūr nilattukku merkkum teṉpār kkellai I
<lb n="17" break="no"/>cceykke pukutap pān=ta vākkālukkum veḷḷāṉū
<lb n="18" break="no"/>r nilattukku vaṭakkum melpāk kellai veḷḷāṉū
<lb n="19" break="no"/>r nilattukkuk kiḻakkum vaṭapār kkellai kiṭaṅkalni
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṉṟum kiḻakku
<lb n="21" break="no"/>nokkip po
<lb n="22" break="no"/>ṉa vāykkālukku
<lb n="23" break="no"/>m veḷḷāṉu<unclear>r</unclear>
<lb n="24"/>nilattukkut ter
<lb n="25" break="no"/>kkum Āka Ivvicai
<lb n="26" break="no"/>tta perunāṉ<note n="506-4">A section after this is built in.</note> 
</p>

